import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import { DefaultCarousel, AlternateCarousel } from "./CarouselComponent"
import { Streamlit } from "streamlit-component-lib"

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <StreamlitProvider>
      <DefaultCarousel />
      <AlternateCarousel />
    </StreamlitProvider>
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById("root")
)
